- "adorned" refers to the characters having equipment.

- "seasoned warriors" refers to characters whose level is greater than 10;
- "wield shards" refers to the relationship between characters and shards through the `character_shards` table;
- "drain more than 5.0 points of magical energy on average" refers to the average MP cost of the shards being greater than 5.0.

